</TEXT>
<NOTE>MIDGETMAN</NOTE>
<TEXT>
 The <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION> accepted <PERSON> Bush </PERSON>'s plan to spend $ 100 million on development of the single-warhead, truck-based missile. The <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> cut all $ 100 million for the Midgetman.
