<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Barry </PERSON> <PERSON> Schweid </PERSON> has covered U.S.-Mideast diplomacy for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> for 16 years.
