w interest bonds to finance the transaction, but later learned that would be prohibited by state law. A plan to borrow $ 75 million then unraveled. `` They simply ran out of cash and had a payroll to meet,'' said <PERSON> Scott </PERSON> <PERSON> Hamilton </PERSON>, editor of Commercial Aviation Week.
